</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
TRAFFIC ACCIDENTS -- NORTHERN CALIFORNIA; POLICE PURSUITS -- NORTHERN 
CALIFORNIA; HIGH SPEED CHASES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA070790-0086 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 243982 </DOCID>
