<HEADLINE>
<P>
CHOCK FULL O' NUTS BUYS PEANUT PACKER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By United Press International 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
NEW YORK 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Chock Full O' Nuts Corp. announced that it has completed the acquisition, 
through its subsidiary Jimbo's Jumbos Inc., of Everfresh Products Inc., a 
processor and packer of in-the-shell peanuts. 
</P>
<P>
The price was not released. 
</P>
<P>
Everfresh, in Erlanger, Ky., sold more than 5 million pounds of peanuts in 
fiscal 1989, the company said. 
</P>
